#. <section class="sutta" id="sn45.153"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn45.153:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 45"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 45"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.153:0.2"
msgid "12. Balakaraṇīyavagga"
msgstr "12. Hard Work"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn45.153:0.3"
msgid "153. Kumbhasutta"
msgstr "153. Pots"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn45.153:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, kumbho nikkujjo vamateva udakaṃ, no paccāvamati;"
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, suppose a pot full of water is tipped over, so the water drains "
"out and doesn’t go back in."

msgctxt "sn45.153:1.2"
msgid ""
"evameva kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bhāvento ariyaṃ "
"aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bahulīkaronto vamateva pāpake akusale dhamme, no "
"paccāvamati."
msgstr ""
"In the same way, a mendicant who develops and cultivates the noble eightfold "
"path expels bad, unskillful qualities and doesn’t let them back in."

msgctxt "sn45.153:1.3"
msgid ""
"Kathañca, bhikkhave, bhikkhu ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bhāvento ariyaṃ "
"aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bahulīkaronto vamateva pāpake akusale dhamme, no "
"paccāvamati?"
msgstr ""
"And how does a mendicant who develops the noble eightfold path expel bad, "
"unskillful qualities and not let them back in?"

msgctxt "sn45.153:1.4"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sammādiṭṭhiṃ bhāveti vivekanissitaṃ virāganissitaṃ "
"nirodhanissitaṃ vossaggapariṇāmiṃ … pe … sammāsamādhiṃ bhāveti "
"vivekanissitaṃ virāganissitaṃ nirodhanissitaṃ vossaggapariṇāmiṃ …"
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant develops right view, right thought, right speech, "
"right action, right livelihood, right effort, right mindfulness, and right "
"immersion, which rely on seclusion, fading away, and cessation, and ripen as "
"letting go."

msgctxt "sn45.153:1.5"
msgid ""
"evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bhāvento ariyaṃ "
"aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bahulīkaronto vamateva pāpake akusale dhamme, no "
"paccāvamatī”ti."
msgstr ""
"That’s how a mendicant who develops and cultivates the noble eightfold path "
"expels bad, unskillful qualities and doesn’t let them back in.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn45.153:1.6"
msgid "Pañcamaṃ."
msgstr ""
